22:25.844 --> 22:27.469
Hoy, FYI...

22:28.847 --> 22:30.932
magkatabi lang ang mga subdivision namin .

22:31.193 --> 22:32.524
Oo, pero...

22:33.393 --> 22:35.145
iba pa din kung nasa iisang school kami .

