Kaya mag-aral!

23:05.592 --> 23:06.718
Nakuha mo ito, Bee!

23:06.718 --> 23:08.695
Madali lang ito, promise!

23:08.720 --> 23:09.846
Focus!

23:09.846 --> 23:11.681
Nandito lang ako para tumulong.

23:11.706 --> 23:13.977
