- Hindi, basahin! Ayan!

23:25.779 --> 23:27.948
Drake, curious lang...

23:30.283 --> 23:33.328
sabi mo gusto mo mas maging
honest ako sayo diba?

23:35.914 --> 23:36.431
Tss.

23:36.456 --> 23:39.543
Totoo ba talagang walang nangyayari
sa inyo ni Tita Katrina?

23:43.839 --> 23:45.090
kasi...

23:45.715 --> 23:48.218
