37:04.121 --> 37:04.906
tama yan!

37:04.931 --> 37:05.640
Nobyembre 31.

37:05.681 --> 37:06.724
Maraming salamat,
salamat, salamat!

37:06.766 --> 37:08.687
Walang November 31, Alys.

37:08.976 --> 37:10.161
Ano bang pinagsasabi mo, syempre meron!

37:10.186 --> 37:11.186
paalam.

37:13.272 --> 37:14.272
